India <br>
China<br>
United States<br>
European Union<br>
<br>
Now, you will have nations that have great influence or economic power, such as:<br>
<br>
Brazil(leader of Mercoser)<br>
Indonesia<br>
Nigeria, the Islamic empire of Africa<br>
Russia, because of the tremendous resources<br>
Pakistan, when allied with Bangladesh and the middle east resources, can be a significant threat.<br>
<br>
